Subject: Meall Buidhe (Corbett) 
To: Laura
Content:
Meall Buidhe is a Corbett situated in the southern highlands of Scotland. It forms part of the ridge line separating Glen Daimh, an offshoot of Glen Lyon from Glen Lyon itself. There is another hill called Meall Buidhe in the Glen Lyon area, about 8km to the northeast. Coordinates: 563410N 43348W / 56.56958N 4.56340W / 56.56958; -4.56340 
